 If you go up here, djtutorial.djfree.com/polls, you see I have a reference implementation.

00:06:30.340 --> 00:06:33.460
 And I have this here so that you don't have to put yours in first.

00:06:33.460 --> 00:06:35.480
 You can see how the autograder works.

00:06:35.480 --> 00:06:36.660
 So I'm gonna press evaluate.

00:06:36.660 --> 00:06:42.500
 Now it didn't take long, but all those requests, and I mentioned that it's trying to tell you

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:43.800
 what's going on.

