 this URL is, cool.

00:07:03.980 --> 00:07:06.060
 Or you can just see the page.

00:07:06.060 --> 00:07:10.380
 If you look at it, what it's showing you is it's showing you it made a request and it's

00:07:10.380 --> 00:07:12.740
