00:07:12.740 --> 00:07:16.540
 And then it looks at that page that got back, and when it looks at the page that came back

00:07:16.540 --> 00:07:19.420
 and it doesn't like it, it tells you about that.

00:07:19.420 --> 00:07:22.660
 And this goes down to I'm trying to give you as much feedback.

